  "lastUpdatedOn": "2013-06-22",
  "religion": "Malkovich is an atheist.",
  "politicalViews": "Malkovich claims to be non-political despite having voted for a Democrat and wanting to fight British Labour politicians to the death.",
  "author": "Tom Kershaw",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 1
    },
    {
      "parentId": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "J"
    },
    {
      "parentId": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "ohn Malkovich was born in Christopher, Illinois and grew up in Benton, Illinois."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 2
    },
    {
      "parentId": 2,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Malkovich is of Croatian descent,",
      "sourceTitle": "ohn Malkovich – Biography",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0000518/bio"
    },
    {
      "parentId": 2,
      "type": "text",
      "text": " a country with an overwhelming Catholic majority.",
      "sourceTitle": "Croatia",
      "sourceUrl": "http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Croatia#Demographics"
    },
    {
      "parentId": 2,
      "type": "text",
      "text": " So, it stands to reason that somewhere in Malkovich's heritage is the Catholic faith."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 3
    },
    {
      "parentId": 3,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "However, Malkovich is an atheist. When asked if one needed religious belief to play spiritual characters, (which Malkovich does on occasion) he responded:"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "id": 4
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 5,
      "parentId": 4
    },
    {
      "parentId": 5,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "No, I'd say not. I'm an atheist. I wouldn't say I'm without spiritual belief particularly, or rather, specifically. Maybe I'm agnostic, but I'm not quite sure there's some great creator somehow controlling everything and giving us free will. I don't know; it doesn't seem to make a lot of sense to me.",
      "sourceTitle": "A kinder, gentler Malkovich",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.thestar.com/entertainment/movies/2008/09/11/a_kinder_gentler_malkovich.html"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 6
    },
    {
      "parentId": 6,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "That's not to say that Malkovich doesn't understand and sympathize with the human drive toward religious or spiritual belief. It just doesn't make sense to him:"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "id": 7
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 8,
      "parentId": 7
    },
    {
      "parentId": 8,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "I think everyone would like to believe there's something immutable or infallible about the human spirit. Everyone would like to believe that, but I'm not sure there's any reason to.",
      "sourceTitle": "A kinder, gentler Malkovich",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.thestar.com/entertainment/movies/2008/09/11/a_kinder_gentler_malkovich.html"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 9
    },
    {
      "parentId": 9,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "There you have it. No reason to believe for Malkovich–so he doesn't.\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "id": 10
    },
    {
      "parentId": 10,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Disputably non-political"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 11
    },
    {
      "parentId": 11,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Malkovich insists that he's not at all political:"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "id": 12
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 13,
      "parentId": 12
    },
    {
      "parentId": 13,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "I'm not a political person actually, and I don't have an ideology. And I don't think other people really think about [my political views].",
      "sourceTitle": "John Malkovich: 'I haven't voted since McGovern lost",
      "sourceUrl": "http://dailycaller.com/2011/06/17/john-malkovich-i-havent-voted-since-mcgovern-lost/"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 14
    },
    {
      "parentId": 14,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "He says he last voted for George McGovern in 1972, a Democratic candidate who lost against Richard Nixon:"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "id": 15
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 16,
      "parentId": 15
    },
    {
      "parentId": 16,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "I haven't voted since McGovern lost and don't intend to. I see no reason to.",
      "sourceTitle": "John Malkovich: 'I haven't voted since McGovern lost",
      "sourceUrl": "http://dailycaller.com/2011/06/17/john-malkovich-i-havent-voted-since-mcgovern-lost/"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 17
    },
    {
      "parentId": 17,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Perhaps that means he lost faith in the political process. However, friends and co-workers such as William Hootkins, disagree, calling Malkovich incredibly \"right-wing.\"",
      "sourceTitle": "John Malkovich: 'I haven't voted since McGovern lost",
      "sourceUrl": "http://dailycaller.com/2011/06/17/john-malkovich-i-havent-voted-since-mcgovern-lost/"
    },
    {
      "parentId": 17,
      "type": "text",
      "text": " And, when Malkovich was asked who he'd like to fight to the death, he mentioned, among others, British Labour politician George Galloway.",
      "sourceTitle": "John Malkovich: 'I haven't voted since McGovern lost",
      "sourceUrl": "http://dailycaller.com/2011/06/17/john-malkovich-i-havent-voted-since-mcgovern-lost/"
    },
    {
      "parentId": 17,
      "type": "text",
      "text": " So maybe right-wing isn't too off base."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 18
    },
    {
      "parentId": 18,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Other than that, Malkovich really does seem non-political. Feel free to weigh in, readers, if you know anything."
    }
  ],
